  4,94,O ona verit ona strike zapricinit GOD ona bol absolutely istota. Nie say do jeden offers ona peace Ona je believer seeking spoils this world For GOD possesses infinite spoils Zapamatat Si ona pouzivat bol them GOD zehnat ona! Therefore ona je absolutely istota ona strike GOD JE fully Cognizant Z everything ONA ROBIT
  4,95,Nie equal som sedentary believers nie handicapped those strive zapricinit GOD ich peniaze ich zivot. GOD exalts strivers ICH PENIAZE ICH ZIVOT above the sedentary. both GOD promises salvation GOD exalts strivers sedentary velky recompense
